data.chText: 三部分的；三人的；三组的
data.enText: having three parts or involving three people or groups

data.chText: 他们正在连演三部恐怖片。
data.enText: They're showing a triple bill of horror movies (= three horror movies one after the other) .
three times as much or as many as sth

data.chText: 他血液中的酒精含量为法定最高限量的三倍。
data.enText: The amount of alcohol in his blood was triple the legal maximum.

data.chText: 它的人口大约是威尼斯的三倍。
data.enText: Its population is about triple that of Venice.
to become, or to make sth, three times as much or as many

data.chText: 到明年产量应增至三倍。
data.enText: Output should triple by next year.

simple_means.memory_skill: tri 三 + ple …倍的 → 三倍的

tr: a base hit at which the batter stops safely at third base
a quantity that is three times as great as another
a set of three similar things considered as a unit
having three units or components or elements
example: a treble row of red beads
triple time has three beats per measure

tr: three times as great or many
example: a claim for treble (or triple) damages

value.def: Triple means consisting of three things or parts.

example.ex: In 1882 Germany, Austria, and Italy formed the Triple Alliance.
example.tran: 1882 年，德国、奥地利和意大利结成了三国同盟。

value.tran: 三个的;三方的;三部分的

value.def: If something triples or if you triple it, it becomes three times as large in size or number.

example.ex: I got a fantastic new job and my salary tripled...
example.tran: 我得到了一份非常好的新工作，薪水涨到了原来的 3 倍。

example.ex: The Exhibition has tripled in size from last year...
example.tran: 展览会规模自去年已经扩至3倍。

example.ex: The merger puts the firm in a position to triple its earnings.
example.tran: 合并可使公司利润增长两倍。

value.def: If something is triple the amount or size of another thing, it is three times as large.

example.ex: The mine reportedly had an accident rate triple the national average...
example.tran: 据报道,该矿事故发生率是全国平均水平的 3 倍。

example.ex: The kitchen is triple the size it once was.
example.tran: 厨房面积扩为原先的 3 倍。

trans: 三相点；三相點；三态点；是三相点；水的三相点
三重威胁；三威胁；三面手；三种威胁；三重威胁制
三向联结构造；三接面；三联点；三结合点；三接点
三连冠；三冠王；三冠；三重冠；三冠赛
三杀（使对方三人出局的决定性举动）

partsOfSpeech.dec: tri 三 + angle 角 → 三角形
tri 三 + atomic 原子的 → 三原子的
tri 三 + color 颜色 → 三色的
tri 三 + enn 年 + ial …的 → 每三年〔一次〕的
tri 三 + later 边 + al …的 → 有三条边的
tri 三 + lingu 语言 + al …的，具有…性质的 → 三种语言的
tri 三 + log 说话 + y 性质，状态，情况，行为 → 分三部来讲 → 三部曲
tri 三 + o 表音乐术语 → 三重奏（唱）
tri 三 + ple …倍的 → 三倍的
tri 三 + pod 脚 → 三脚架
tri 三 + section 部分 →〔相等的〕三个部分 → 三等分
tri 三 + syllable 音节 → 三音节词
du 二 + ple …倍的 → 两倍的
quadru〔= quadri四〕+ ple …倍的 → 四倍的
tri 三 + ple …倍的 → 三倍的
